<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Verify Your Email</title>
    <style>
      body {
        background-color: #f5f7fa;
        font-family: "Segoe UI", Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        background: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 12px;
        box-shadow: 0 3px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        padding: 40px;
      }

      h2 {
        color: #333333;
        text-align: center;
      }

      p {
        color: #555555;
        line-height: 1.6;
        font-size: 15px;
      }

      .otp-box {
        background: #f0f4ff;
        border: 2px dashed #4a90e2;
        color: #1a3c8b;
        font-size: 24px;
        font-weight: bold;
        letter-spacing: 4px;
        text-align: center;
        padding: 20px;
        margin: 25px 0;
        border-radius: 10px;
      }

      .footer {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #999999;
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 30px;
      }

      .logo {
        display: block;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 30px;
      }

      .logo img {
        height: 60px;
      }

      .highlight {
        color: #007bff;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <div class="logo">
        <img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/3/3b/Logo_Blue.png" alt="E-Shop Logo" />
      </div>

      <h2>Email Verification Required</h2>

      <p>Hi <span class="highlight"><%= name %></span>,</p>

      <p>
        Thank you for registering with <strong>E-Shop</strong>!  
        To complete your registration and verify your email address, please use the following one-time password (OTP):
      </p>

      <div class="otp-box"><%= otp %></div>

      <p>
        This OTP will expire in <strong>5 minutes</strong>.  
        Please do not share it with anyone for security reasons.
      </p>

      <p>
        If you did not request this email, you can safely ignore it â€” your account will remain inactive.
      </p>

      <div class="footer">
        &copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> E-Shop. All rights reserved.
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
